<plot>The two talking-magpies, Heckle and Jeckle, are observing the crowds going into the theater to see a performance of "The Barber of Seville" and decide to get some culture of their own by attending the opera by sneaking in, of course. The stage-door manager tosses them out on their first attempt but they finally get by him, and have a typical H&amp;J outing by running across the stage during the performance, changing into costumes and evading the frantic efforts of the manager.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?407746</url></doc>
